\displaystyle \sum_n n^2
\sum_{k=1}^n k^2\sim \int_1^n x^2dx=\frac{1}{3}\left[x^3\right]_1^n\sim\frac{n^3}{3},
\lim_{\infty}\frac{1}{n^3}\sum_{k=1}^n k^2=\frac{1}{3}.
